snippet.title: Johnny Depp Analysis Documentary / Interviews
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp Amber Heard Analysis Biography Documentary
I analyze Johnny Depp's famous / notorious 2018 interviews with Rolling Stone and GQ magazines for better insights into his life , biography , and the Amber Heard situation.

Check out my other videos on Depp and Amber Heard and other celebrity controversies, and subscribe to my channel. 

My next video will be on the Woody Allen controversy, then I will make a follow-up video to my Marilyn Manson documentaries. Please subscribe.
